sbuild was originally packaged for Debian by Rick Younie <younie@debian.org>.

sbuild is currently maintained by the Debian buildd-tools project.  It
was downloaded from
svn://svn.debian.org/svn/buildd-tools/trunk/sbuild

The upstream source was originally downloaded from
:pserver:anon@cvs.linux-m68k.org:/CVS (module: wanna-build)
(up to version 0.36; September 2006)
http://svn.cyberhqz.com/svn/wanna-build
(version 0.37; January 2006 to present)

Authors:
Roman Hodek - wanna-build (and sbuild)
Ben Collins - the "apt patch" for sbuild for finding source
Ryan Murray - modifications for security building, maintenance
Roger Leigh - schroot support and general maintenance

